00:00:18.535 --> 00:00:20.701
Today, let's prepare Star Chicken!

00:00:22.927 --> 00:00:24.956
Ingredients required to prepare Star Chicken: 

00:00:25.421 --> 00:00:29.888
Chicken, Garam Masala, Yogurt, Gram Flour, Corn Flour

00:00:30.223 --> 00:00:33.889
Oil, Turmeric powder, Salt, Ginger-Garlic paste

00:00:34.250 --> 00:00:37.844
Egg, Green Chillies, Lemon, Coriander leaves.

00:00:45.227 --> 00:00:46.775
Shift the Chicken to a broad content.

00:00:49.092 --> 00:00:54.911
Add Red Chilli powder, Salt to taste &amp; 
a pinch of Turmeric powder.

00:00:58.018 --> 00:01:01.530
Add Garam Masala &amp; Ginger-Garlic paste.

00:01:09.269 --> 00:01:11.025
Add 2 Tbsp Yogurt.

00:01:17.607 --> 00:01:19.777
Add the Lemon juice.

00:01:23.244 --> 00:01:27.110
Add finely chopped Green Chillies &amp; Coriander leaves.

00:01:29.965 --> 00:01:32.576
Mix the ingredients well.

00:01:39.438 --> 00:01:42.411
Marinate the Chicken for 20 mins.

00:01:47.559 --> 00:01:51.143
Heat Oil in a pan for deep frying.

00:01:55.381 --> 00:01:57.643
Add 2 Tbsp Gram flour to the marinated Chicken.
Note : Gram Flour to be added before frying.

00:02:06.135 --> 00:02:08.348
Add 1 Tbsp Corn flour.
Note : Corn Flour to be added before frying.

00:02:18.989 --> 00:02:22.167
Add 1 Egg to this.
Note : Egg to be added to the marinated Chicken.

00:02:29.489 --> 00:02:31.956
Mix the contents well.

00:02:40.695 --> 00:02:44.588
Deep fry the Chicken pieces till golden brown.

00:02:47.509 --> 00:02:49.352
Shift the Star Chicken to a serving bowl.
Garnish with Onions &amp; Tomatoes.

